name: ***SOLD OUT***      Hand Painted Kerr Jars - Sea Breeze collection
description:
Quart size Kerr wide mouth jars, hand painted and distressed for a shabby, vintage, beach or cottage look. 

Each Jar has a removable lid piece to allow flowers etc to be placed in them with the appearance of the lid being on.

These jars are fabulous as unique decorative pieces in the home or for use as wedding centrepieces, or for party decorations.

Each jar is painted with a water resistant enamel, so they may be gently cleaned with a damp towel, however submerging in water or the dishwasher is NOT recommended.

Measurements - each jar is 16.5cm H X 9cm W

*Flowers not included*
